# Asset Tracking Device Simulation

## Overview
This C program simulates an asset tracking device that:
- Generates random temperature and GPS data.
- Packages the data into a compact binary payload.
- Displays the payload as a hex-encoded string.
- (Bonus) Parses a downlink hex message to update the reporting interval.

## Compilation
gcc main.c payload.c -o asset_tracking

## Running
./asset_tracking

